# Globs the loop may not write, once armed via `.claude/verify/run.sh --gt-approve`.
# This file stays `.pending` (unarmed) until a human runs --gt-approve — arming too early would
# block the authoring pass itself. No ground-truth/** entry: this project is `lite` tier (see
# planning/00-master-plan.md) — there is no ground-truth/ directory at all.
.claude/verify/checks.yaml
.claude/verify/run.sh
.claude/verify/integrity.sh
.claude/verify/_runner.py
.claude/integrity/protected.txt
*.config.*
